  <VFEE_GrandBall.questContentRules.rulesStrings.30>raidArrivedLetterText-&gt;A group of deserters have arrived to attempt to disrupt the grand ball and assasinate the royals\n\n[asker_nameFull] does not care for the threat and demands the ball continues!  [asker_possessive] wants you too keep them safe and deal with the &quot;peasants&quot;.</VFEE_GrandBall.questContentRules.rulesStrings.30>
  <VFEE_GrandBall.questContentRules.rulesStrings.31>BallSuccessLetterLetterLabel-&gt;GrandBall Success</VFEE_GrandBall.questContentRules.rulesStrings.31>
  <VFEE_GrandBall.questContentRules.rulesStrings.32>BallSuccessLetterText-&gt;The shuttle has departed with [asker_nameFull] and [asker_possessive] guests. Overall the event was a success and everyone made it back safe.</VFEE_GrandBall.questContentRules.rulesStrings.32>
